sentences: Reginald Quincy Arvizu (born November 2, 1969),  also known as "Fieldy", is an American musician, best known as the bassist for nu metal band Korn.
In August 2012 it was reported that Fieldy would be taking a brief break from Korn as his wife Dena was expecting a child.
Korn began touring through Eastern Europe, Russia and India throughout August and September 2012 with fill-in bassist Ryan Martinie from Mudvayne.
